Head and abdomen pale; thorax pale, with vittae and scutum stramineous. Legs pale.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="32.[151,1436,359,695]" pageId="32" pageNumber="33">
<emphasis box="[199,267,498,523]" italics="true" pageId="32" pageNumber="33">Head.</emphasis>
